    "description": "Set in a bizarre yet wonderful world, Liam_99 is a <strong>story-driven, adventure and exploration game.</strong> You’ll play as - <i>and sometimes alongside</i> - <strong>Liam,</strong> a skeleton who lost every memories of his past life... <strong>but still knows he's the main character of a video game!</strong><br><br>Helping Liam remember who he was will require you to overcome <strong>four major adventures,</strong> each one very different from the others - <strong>in terms of environment and ambiance as well as gameplay-wise.</strong> Brace yourself for <strong>various challenges</strong> such as <strong>obstacle races</strong> or <strong>puzzles,</strong> exalted with a <strong>touch of 4th wall-breaking and absurd jokes!</strong><br><br>In addition to these four adventures, Liam_99 shall let you <strong>roam freely a world full of wonders and secrets.</strong> Discover <strong>famous works of art</strong> (anew), plunder <strong>treasure chests</strong> and collect <strong>strange keys,</strong> venture <strong>deep underground…</strong> or have a moment to take in the view and appreciate Liam’s jokes. <i>Whatever works best for you!</i><br><br><strong>Liam_99 aims to offer a refreshing, carefully designed experience.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288190/extras/686752c8d69370669a87a718e3d2c020.poster.avif?t=1682514735\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288190/extras/686752c8d69370669a87a718e3d2c020.webm?t=1682514735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288190/extras/686752c8d69370669a87a718e3d2c020.mp4?t=1682514735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game shall be fully voice-acted in French, as well as in English - if the crowdfunding 