mp4?t=1682514735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you think that Death is restful, you may change your mind after playing the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ADDITIONAL FEATURES</h2><br><br>- An open afterworld to explore<br><br>- Many cutscenes to skip (please don't)<br><br>- A day/night cycle and weather system",
